{"tid":2118993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如疫苗未試清楚, 急於推出, 會唔會發生現實版［Biohazard］或［Resident Evil］𠺢?","createTime":"2020-07-22T00:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T01:03:20.000Z","uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a68a423e9860ea92e4efc8ab196d18d7dc5349ed","tid":2118993,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"各國為重開經濟, 急於研發「舞廢濕狗」疫苗及想盡快推出應用。<br />\n如疫苗未試清楚, 急於推出, 會唔會發生現實版［Biohazard］或［Resident Evil］𠺢?<br />\n到時大部份人會被感染, 變成藍色喪屍(簡稱:藍屍)； 721又會唔見人, 因已3萬thx左。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n1) 衛生署係唔係, 唔敢公佈三位或四位中招數字, 一來, 化驗唔切, 二來, 只報確診幾十單及另報初步確診又幾十單, 其實質就係一日百幾單無異喇!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 琴日, 正苦澄清不可能在未來數天實施所謂「禁足令」, 甘是否在需要時, 仍會考慮實施「禁足令」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c8c2dfc484bc8220cc5e4bd18a29897ee28c24","tid":2118993,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"都係老人家打姐<br />\n驚西"},{"pid":"761e748b5addc7f3986f32420db153376a12acdf","tid":2118993,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"而家得大陸跳過phase III ，直接俾解放軍打"},{"pid":"e95b53e0f09bbaf8dc9d558457018d24e5ace9c3","tid":2118993,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761e748b5addc7f3986f32420db153376a12acdf","tid":2118993,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"而家得大陸跳過phase III ，直接俾解放軍打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:00:24.000Z",